data.description: Wow!! Stunning 4bedroom 3 bath with a gameroom/den home located in the desired area Taylor's Landing Beaumont Tx. The Cove at Taylor Landing is a beautiful community located in Beaumont with easy access to the highway. This community features low taxes and zoned to Hamshire-Fannett School District, a top ranked school district. As you walk into this beautiful open concept living room that flows into the kitchen.  The large master bedroom is connected with a grand master bathroom that has a walk-in shower, double sinks, jetted tub. You will not want to miss out on the property. Schedule a tour today! Buyer to do their own measurements. Survey on file.
